OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780308639
OL,3,CE-bike rider stabbed victim to death
OL,4,Cin underpass
OL,6,FA man who killed a 22-year-old with a
OL,7,Fsingle stab in an underpass and then
OL,8,Ffled the scene on an e-bike has been
OL,9,Ffound guilty of manslaughter.
OL,11,FMarley Gascoine died on 10 November
OL,12,F2025 after being attacked in the St
OL,13,FAnn's area of Nottingham.
OL,15,FMatthew Smith, 20, fled the scene on
OL,16,Fan electric bike, leaving his victim
OL,17,Fto stumble away and collapse outside
OL,18,Fan address in Abbotsford Drive.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
