FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780308639
OL,3,CE-bike rider stabbed victim to death
OL,4,Cin underpass
OL,6,FA jury at Nottingham Crown Court found
OL,7,FSmith guilty of manslaughter following
OL,8,Fa three-week trial.
OL,10,FHe will be sentenced on 7 September
OL,11,F2026.
OL,13,FPolice say that the men were part of a
OL,14,Fgroup in the vicinity of the underpass
OL,15,Ffrom around midday on the day of the
OL,16,Fattack.
OL,18,FThe two were seen on CCTV exchanging
OL,19,Fwords before moments later the victim
OL,20,Fshouted out in pain and stumbled out
OL,21,Fof the underpass
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780308639
OL,3,CE-bike rider stabbed victim to death
OL,4,Cin underpass
OL,6,FInvestigations revealed that Smith
OL,7,Fthen travelled on an e-bike to a house
OL,8,Fin nearby Little John Walk.
OL,10,FHe left the address on foot a short
OL,11,Ftime later, wearing different clothes
OL,12,Fwhich were clearly too small for him,
OL,13,Fin an attempt to alter his appearance.
OL,15,FDetectives also discovered Smith and
OL,16,Fothers had disposed of the weapon, a
OL,17,Flarge knife, and clothing, as well as
OL,18,Fremoving the distinctive handlebars on
OL,19,Fhis e-bike.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
