FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780308639
OL,3,CE-bike rider stabbed victim to death
OL,4,Cin underpass
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Ruby Burrow,
OL,7,Fwho led the investigation, said:
OL,9,F"After months of falsely claiming he'd
OL,10,Facted in self defence, Matthew Smith
OL,11,Fhas now been convicted of manslaughter.
OL,13,F"His actions that day have not only
OL,14,Ftaken Marley's life but also ruined
OL,15,Fhis own and those of many other people
OL,16,Fconnected with both men.
OL,18,F"We see time and again how
OL,19,Fdisagreements become more serious for
OL,20,Fall concerned simply because of the
OL,21,Fpresence of a knife.
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@AOU
